<div id="review_228175253" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/228175253" />
    <a title="Tory Wagner" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6192327-tory-wagner"><img alt="Tory Wagner" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1314996961p2/6192327.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/228175253?book_show_action=true">Oct 27, 2011</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Tory Wagner" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Tory Wagner" href="/user/show/6192327-tory-wagner">Tory Wagner</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6192327-tory-wagner?shelf=science-fiction">science-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6192327-tory-wagner?shelf=aventure">aventure</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer228175253" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3639942782831345935">I really enjoyed the descriptions of New Mexico with the desert and the mountainous areas. The scenario of a deadly flu seems very realisitic. I know through some geneology research that epidemics such as flu and diphtheria have been very common throughout history. The description of a virtual world that was created displaying scenes and people sound like technology that is currently available perhaps on a more sophisticated level. Alot of action and some interesting characters make for a good a</span>
  <span id="freeText3639942782831345935" style="display:none">I really enjoyed the descriptions of New Mexico with the desert and the mountainous areas. The scenario of a deadly flu seems very realisitic. I know through some geneology research that epidemics such as flu and diphtheria have been very common throughout history. The description of a virtual world that was created displaying scenes and people sound like technology that is currently available perhaps on a more sophisticated level. Alot of action and some interesting characters make for a good adventure. The only negative was the rather contrived nature of the main character's family background.</span>
  <a data-text-id="3639942782831345935" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
