        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer80810225" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14121685177200326414">This being their second book together (first after their Pendergast debut) is more of a medical/techo thriller. Lots of that jargon also. But, later in the story, and the part three ending, you get more of their adventure action your used to seeing. Not one of their best, but enjoyable getaway. 3.5 stars.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


